frequently comes down to having to make decisions whether they can pay their medical bills buy food or buy medicine may said the power to care exists to help ensure the most vulnerable among us dont have to face that choice may presented the ceremonial check to customers who received help through the power to care program they used the opportunity to express their appreciation for the assistance i am so thankful for the help provided by the power to care said joan bradley of river ridge i had a medical emergency and needed help paying my utility bill i am very grateful for the assistance i received through the program to derricka griffin the program is an important emergency lifeline for senior citizens like her mother alita griffin of river ridge the power to care is much needed especially for seniors like my mother who live on a fixed income and can find themselves short on bills the cost of living keeps increasing but it seems like the fixed incomes seniors receive are staying the same if there is an unexpected expense it puts them in a real bind derricka griffin said on hand for the event were state sen conrad appel rmetairie state rep kirk talbot r river ridge state rep polly thomas rmetairie jefferson parish councilman paul johnson harahan mayor tina miceli and members of the jefferson council on aging board of directors the power to care program is funded by contributions from customers employees and shareholders to donate to the power to care or for more information click here one of the ways to help fund the program is by participating in the annual the power to care charity golf tournament this years golf tournament is scheduled for oct  at the university club of baton rouge sponsorships and teams are still available please contact nicole grille at  for information entergy louisiana llc provides electric service to more than  million customers and natural gas service to more than  customers in the greater baton rouge area with operations in southern central and northeastern louisiana the company is a subsidiary of entergy corporation entergy corporation is an integrated energy company engaged primarily in electric power production and retail distribution operations entergy owns and operates power plants with approximately  megawatts of electric generating capacity including nearly  megawatts of nuclear power entergy delivers electricity to  million utility customers in arkansas louisiana mississippi and texas entergy has annual revenues of approximately  billion and nearly  employees  entergylouisianacomfacebookcomentergyla twitter entergyla  entergy corporation published this content on  july  and is solely responsible for the information contained herein distributed by public unedited and unaltered on  july   utc original documenthttpwwwentergynewsroomcomlatestnewsentergylouisianadonatesthepowertocare public permalinkhttpwwwpublicnowcomviewaebddebb  latest news on entergy corporation p pilgrim nuclear power station tailg  pilgrim workers deliberately violated s p entergy  no council pushes back deadline on m entergy power plant  entergy  announces second quarter earnings conference call  entergy  rolls out  in grants to fuel stronger communities in mississipp  entergy  louisiana to bring advanced meters to homes and businesses  pilgrim nuclear power station tailg  pilgrim workers deliberately violated s  entergy  plymouth  two workers at the pilgrim nuclear power station in plymout  entergy  louisiana donates  to the power to care  nrc  pilgrim workers deliberately violated security procedures  stantec  kemp bottom road bridge closed more news news from seekingalpha  beat the market with more dividends and less volatility  entergy gains approval to build lake charles power station in louisiana  why im buying this dividend etf  game plan for the week  cramers mad money   wall street breakfast  look out below oil is growling financials  sales    m ebit    m net income   m debt    m yield   pe ratio   pe ratio   ev  s