ion with its appropriate pool pump speed the energy saved is considerable reducing pump speed by onehalf allows the pump to use just oneeighth as much energy entergy solutions offers a  rebate for a newlyinstalled variable speed pool pump click here for a  pool pump rebate application form any residential entergy louisiana customer is eligible to receive a rebate for an energy star rated pool pump installed in an inground pool contact a pool professional to purchase and install an energy star pool pumps apply for the entergy solutions rebate here window acs energy star® window air conditioner program click here for the mailin rebate application increase your homes comfort while reducing monthly energy bills by installing a new high efficiency window air conditioner ac entergy solutions provides mailin rebates for the purchase and installation of energy efficient window units any residential entergy louisiana customer is eligible to receive rebates for energy star qualified units purchased from a participating retailer each customer can receive rebates for up to four window units visit any of the entergy solutions retail partners to purchase a new energy star window unit or any retailer who sells energy star window units at the time of sale you will receive a rebate application please complete the application and send to entergy solutions within  days of the purchase if not available from the retailer applications can be downloaded here the installation will then be confirmed and the rebate will be mailed to you within three weeks rebates are offered on a firstcome firstserved basis and funding is limited additional eligible tax credits or rebates may be available all energy star qualified window units are eligible for a  mailin rebate led light bulbs save up to  per bulb on led light bulbs emitting very little heat and averaging  years in lifespan highlyefficient led bulbs use as little as six watts of energy  compared to  watts with a traditional incandescent bulb 