installation of the advanced meters this timeline is based on experiences from other utilities that have modernized their power grids meter installation will begin in early  and by the end of  homes and businesses in the entergy louisiana service area can be part of a smarter energy future learn more about our vision here entergylouisianaams entergy louisianas more than  natural gas customers in the greater baton rouge area also will have their gas meters upgraded with new technology that will provide customers with data needed to better manage gas usage and help lower bills entergy louisiana llc provides electric service to more than  million customers and natural gas service to more than  customers in the greater baton rouge area with operations in southern central and northeastern louisiana the company is a subsidiary of entergy corporation entergy corporation is an integrated energy company engaged primarily in electric power production and retail distribution operations entergy owns and operates power plants with approximately  megawatts of electric generating capacity including nearly  megawatts of nuclear power entergy delivers electricity to  million utility customers in arkansas louisiana mississippi and texas entergy has annual revenues of approximately  billion and nearly  employees  entergylouisianacom facebookcomentergyla twitter entergyla  entergy corporation published this content on  july  and is solely responsible for the information contained herein distributed by public unedited and unaltered on  july   utc original documenthttpwwwentergynewsroomcomlatestnewsentergylouisianabringadvancedmetershomesbusinesses public permalinkhttpwwwpublicnowcomviewbfedccffaddcfdeefce cartlatest newsall american usc footbal player joseph m boskovich jr now picks all american value stocks for his clientspaul hogan picks tech dividend growers microchip technology nasdaqmchp xilinx nasdaqxlnx and versum materials nysevsm gallons of water to produce a mcdonalds nysemcd 